data.description: STUNNING TWO-STORY HOME SET ON OVER SIX ACRES IN SHEFFIELD PLANTATION WITH A GATED ENTRANCE AND CIRCULAR DRIVEWAY.  THE EXTERIOR IS CONSTRUCTED OF CYPRESS BOARD & BATTEN AND INCLUDES A SCREENED LANAI, OPEN DECK, ABOVE GROUND POOL, OUTDOOR SHOWER, STORAGE BUILDING, & MORE.  STEP INSIDE TO HEART OF PINE HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT THE MAIN LEVEL.  YOU WILL LOVE THE ARCHITECTURE IN THE TWO-STORY FOYER & SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM WITH CYPRESS TONGUE & GROOVE CEILINGS AND AN ABUNDANCE OF NATURAL LIGHT.  THE EXPANSIVE KITCHEN OFFERS A BREAKFAST BAR AND STAINLESS APPLIANCES IN ADDITION TO PLENTY OF PREP SPACE & STORAGE GALORE.  THE PRIMARY BEDROOM SUITE IS LOCATED ON THE MAIN LEVEL AND FEATURES A FREESTANDING TUB AND SEPARATE SHOWER- THIS ROOM CONNECTS TO A BONUS ROOM THAT WOULD MAKE A GREAT OFFICE, NURSERY, FITNESS ROOM, ETC.  THE MAIN LEVEL ALSO INCLUDES A FORMAL DINING ROOM, LAUNDRY, AND A HALF BATH.  UPSTAIRS YOU WILL FIND TWO OVERSIZED BEDROOMS AND A FULL BATH.  THE LARGE BONUS ROOM IS LOCATED ABOVE THE ATTACHED TWO-CAR GARAGE.   LOCATED MINUTES FROM I-95, ENJOY EASY ACCESS TO SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, AND DINING.  NO CITY TAXES AND NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED.  THIS PROPERTY IS ZONED FOR HORSES AND THE ROADS ARE MAINTAINED BY THE COUNTY.
